<pb ed="T" id="T24.1457.0520c" n="0520c"/>
<lb n="0520c01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0520c02"/><head type="no">No. 1457</head>
<lb n="0520c03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead>根本說一切有部<note n="0520022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔略〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0520022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔略〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0520022"><lem>略</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>毘奈耶雜事
<lb n="0520c04"/>攝頌<note n="0520023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0520023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0520023"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0520c05"/>
<lb n="0520c06"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0520024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三藏法師＝大唐三藏【宋】【元】【宮】，唐三藏【明】</note><note n="0520024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三藏法師＝大唐三藏【宋】【元】【宮】，＝唐三藏【明】</note><app n="0520024"><lem>三藏法師</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">大唐三藏</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">唐三藏</rdg></app>義淨奉　制譯</byline>
<lb n="0520c07"/><div1 type="jing"><p>此<note n="0520025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雜＝近【明】</note><app n="0520025"><lem>雜</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">近</rdg></app>事中總有八門。以大門一頌攝盡宏綱
<lb n="0520c08"/>一一門中各有別門。總攝八頌就別門中各
<lb n="0520c09"/>有十頌。合九十頌。并內攝頌向有千行。若能
<lb n="0520c10"/>讀<note n="0520026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＝頌【明】</note><app n="0520026"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">頌</rdg></app>憶持者。即可總閑其義。</p>
<lb n="0520c11"/><p>大門總攝頌曰<note place="inline">總有八頌攝</note>。</p>
<lb n="0520c12"/><lg><l>&CB00513;石及牛毛</l><l>三衣并上座</l>
<lb n="0520c13"/><l>舍利猛獸筋</l><l>笈多尼除塔</l></lg>
<lb n="0520c14"/><p>第一別門總攝頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0520c15"/><lg><l>&CB00513;揩剪爪&CB00425;</l><l>鏡生支蹈衣</l>
<lb n="0520c16"/><l>水羅生豆殊</l><l>洗足裙應結</l></lg>
<lb n="0520c17"/><p>別門子攝頌十行。</p>
<lb n="0520c18"/><lg><l>&CB00513;揩石白土</l><l>牛黃香益眼</l>
<lb n="0520c19"/><l>打柱等諸緣</l><l>瓔珞即應知</l>
<lb n="0520c20"/><l>剪爪髮揩光</l><l>春時&CB00290;小果</l>
<lb n="0520c21"/><l>渴聽五種藥</l><l>廣說大生緣</l>
<lb n="0520c22"/><l>綴&CB00425;畜資具</l><l>刀子及針筒</l>
<lb n="0520c23"/><l>并以&CB01856;有三</l><l>是大仙開許</l>
<lb n="0520c24"/><l>照鏡并鑒水</l><l>不應用梳刷</l>
<lb n="0520c25"/><l>頂上留長髮</l><l>浴室栗&CB01754;毘</l>
<lb n="0520c26"/><l>生支當護面</l><l>不為歌舞樂</l>
<lb n="0520c27"/><l>許作歌詠聲</l><l>用&CB00425;有四種</l>
<lb n="0520c28"/><l>蹈衣并諸袋</l><l>褥及於坐具</l>
<lb n="0520c29"/><l>有緣離三衣</l><l>六種心念法</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T24.1457.0521a" n="0521a"/>
<lb n="0521a01"/><l>水羅有五種</l><l>器共一衣食</l>
<lb n="0521a02"/><l>露形噉飲食</l><l>洗浴事應知</l>
<lb n="0521a03"/><l>豆生不淨地</l><l>吐食指授索</l>
<lb n="0521a04"/><l>銅器不應為</l><l>盛鹽等隨畜</l>
<lb n="0521a05"/><l>應為洗足處</l><l>及以濯足盆</l>
<lb n="0521a06"/><l>熱時須扇風</l><l>蚊蟲開五拂</l>
<lb n="0521a07"/><l>結下裙不高</l><l>不持於重擔</l>
<lb n="0521a08"/><l>若病許杖絡</l><l>服蒜等隨聽</l></lg>
<lb n="0521a09"/><p>第二別門總攝頌曰<note n="0521001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔十行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521001"><lem><note place="inline">十行</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0521a10"/><lg><l>牛毛并傘蓋</l><l>披緂勝鬘緣</l>
<lb n="0521a11"/><l>出家藥湯瓶</l><l>門扇鎚斤斧</l></lg>
<lb n="0521a12"/><p>別門子攝頌十行。</p>
<lb n="0521a13"/><lg><l>牛毛及隱處</l><l>同床不獨<note n="0521002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">披＝被【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">披＝被【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521002"><lem>披</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">被</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0521a14"/><l>若得白色衣</l><l>染覆方應用</l>
<lb n="0521a15"/><l>傘蓋無後世</l><l>歌聲不放火</l>
<lb n="0521a16"/><l>遊行覓依止</l><l>毛緂不翻披</l>
<lb n="0521a17"/><l>披緂聽不聽</l><l>惡聲不置&CB00425;</l>
<lb n="0521a18"/><l>衣開<note n="0521003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三種紐＝五種紉【明】</note><app n="0521003"><lem>三種紐</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">五種紉</rdg></app></l><l>應知<note n="0521004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">條＝修【宮】</note><app n="0521004"><lem>條</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">修</rdg></app>亦三</l>
<lb n="0521a19"/><l>勝鬘惡生事</l><l>次制諸瓔珞</l>
<lb n="0521a20"/><l>金<note n="0521005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">條＝絛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">條＝絛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521005"><lem>條</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">絛</rdg></app>及彩物</l><l>斯皆不應畜</l>
<lb n="0521a21"/><l>出家有五利</l><l>不捉錢授學</l>
<lb n="0521a22"/><l>大眾說伽他</l><l>&CB00195;<note n="0521006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">筩＝筒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">筩＝筒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521006"><lem>筩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">筒</rdg></app>漱聽許</l>
<lb n="0521a23"/><l>藥湯應洗浴</l><l>灌鼻開銅盞</l>
<lb n="0521a24"/><l>乘輿老病聽</l><l>須知便利事</l>
<lb n="0521a25"/><l>水瓶知淨觸</l><l>願世尊長壽</l>
<lb n="0521a26"/><l>因斯尼涅槃</l><l>噉嚼俱開五</l>
<lb n="0521a27"/><l>安門扇<note n="0521007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01894;＝鈕【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01894;＝鈕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521007"><lem>&CB01894;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">鈕</rdg></app>孔</l><l>皮替處中&CB00275;</l>
<lb n="0521a28"/><l>內闊網扇樞</l><l>開<note n="0521008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">店＝扂【宋】【宮】，居【元】【明】</note><note n="0521008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">店＝扂【宋】【宮】，＝居【元】【明】</note><app n="0521008"><lem>店</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">扂</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">居</rdg></app>須<note n="0521009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羊＝半【宮】</note><app n="0521009"><lem>羊</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">半</rdg></app>甲</l>
<lb n="0521a29"/><l>鐵鎚及鎗子</l><l>鐵<note n="0521010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01916;＝插【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01916;＝插【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521010"><lem>&CB01916;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">插</rdg></app>并木杴</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T24.1457.0521b" n="0521b"/>
<lb n="0521b01"/><l>釜床&CB01105;五百</l><l>斧鑿眾皆許</l>
<lb n="0521b02"/><l>許斤斧三梯</l><l>竹木繩隨事</l>
<lb n="0521b03"/><l>下灌造寺法</l><l>說難<note n="0521011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＝陀【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他＝陀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521011"><lem>他</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">陀</rdg></app>因緣</l></lg>
<lb n="0521b04"/><p>第三別門總攝頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0521b05"/><lg><l>三衣及衣架</l><l>河邊造寺鹽</l>
<lb n="0521b06"/><l>拭面拭身巾</l><l>寺座刀應畜</l></lg>
<lb n="0521b07"/><p>別門子攝頌十行。</p>
<lb n="0521b08"/><lg><l>三衣條葉量</l><l>床&CB00560;拂遊塵</l>
<lb n="0521b09"/><l>行處著&CB01071;&CB00544;</l><l><note n="0521012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">扞＝&CB01798;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">扞＝&CB01798;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521012"><lem>扞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB01798;</rdg></app>石須時畜</l>
<lb n="0521b10"/><l>衣架及燈籠</l><l>勿使蟲傷損</l>
<lb n="0521b11"/><l>熱開三面舍</l><l>可記難陀身</l>
<lb n="0521b12"/><l>河邊制齒木</l><l>羅怙遣出門</l>
<lb n="0521b13"/><l>合訶不合訶</l><l>二行應與服</l>
<lb n="0521b14"/><l>造寺安簷網</l><l>廣陳掃地緣</l>
<lb n="0521b15"/><l>求法說二童</l><l>熱時聽造舍</l>
<lb n="0521b16"/><l>石鹽安<note n="0521013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">角＝筒【宮】</note><app n="0521013"><lem>角</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">筒</rdg></app>內</l><l>藥器用&CB01071;&CB00544;</l>
<lb n="0521b17"/><l>安替誦經時</l><l>以物承其足</l>
<lb n="0521b18"/><l>拭面巾&CB00520;薄</l><l>唾盆并襯體</l>
<lb n="0521b19"/><l>鐵槽砌基地</l><l>日光珠浣衣</l>
<lb n="0521b20"/><l>拭身履<note n="0521014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蛇＝地【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蛇＝地【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521014"><lem>蛇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">地</rdg></app>咽</l><l>石器生疑惑</l>
<lb n="0521b21"/><l>染衣有多種</l><l>隨意盡伽藍</l>
<lb n="0521b22"/><l>造寺所須物</l><l>穿床禮敬儀</l>
<lb n="0521b23"/><l>別畜剃<note n="0521015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">髮＝鬘【元】【明】</note><app n="0521015"><lem>髮</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">鬘</rdg></app>衣</l><l>花<note n="0521016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬘＝髮【元】【明】</note><app n="0521016"><lem>鬘</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">髮</rdg></app><note n="0521017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">掛＝挂【宮】</note><app n="0521017"><lem>掛</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">挂</rdg></app>眠處</l>
<lb n="0521b24"/><l>好座并床施</l><l>香泥及&CB00425;籠</l>
<lb n="0521b25"/><l>油器法語行</l><l>衣袋持三索</l>
<lb n="0521b26"/><l>須剃刀應畜</l><l>及剪甲等物</l>
<lb n="0521b27"/><l>支床并偃<note n="0521018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枕＝机【三】</note><note n="0521018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">枕＝机【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0521018"><lem>枕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">机</rdg></app></l><l>香土用隨情</l></lg>
<lb n="0521b28"/><p>第四別門總攝頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0521b29"/><lg><l>上座及牆柵</l><l>緣破并養病</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T24.1457.0521c" n="0521c"/>
<lb n="0521c01"/><l>旃荼&CB00337;蔗寺</l><l>&CB00425;依栽樹法</l></lg>
<lb n="0521c02"/><p>別門子攝頌十行。</p>
<lb n="0521c03"/><lg><l>上座翻次說</l><l>或可共至終</l>
<lb n="0521c04"/><l>濾作非時漿</l><l>處不為限齊</l>
